data.eml:eml: Four new records of Conidae (Mollusca: Caenogastropoda) from the Andaman Islands, India

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Franklin, J. Benjamin, Venkateshwaran, P., Vinithkumar, N. V., Kirubagaran, R. (2013): Four new records of Conidae (Mollusca: Caenogastropoda) from the Andaman Islands, India. Zootaxa 3635 (1): 81-86, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3635.1.8
